trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when a SharePoint command fails.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 命令失败时引发的异常。

trans-unit.source: *SharePoint commands* are methods that can be used in a SharePoint tools extension to call into the SharePoint server object model.
trans-unit.target: *SharePoint 命令*是可以用于在 SharePoint 工具扩展中调入 SharePoint 服务器对象模型的方法。

trans-unit.source: SharePoint commands are executed by a 64-bit process named vssphost4.exe.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 命令都由名为 vssphost4.exe 的 64 位进程执行。

trans-unit.source: Any exception raised in vssphost4.exe is returned to the SharePoint command as a <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException>.
trans-unit.target: 在 vssphost4.exe 中引发任何异常返回到 SharePoint 命令的访问权限<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException>。

trans-unit.source: For more information about SharePoint commands, see [Calling into the SharePoint Object Models](/visualstudio/sharepoint/calling-into-the-sharepoint-object-models.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关 SharePoint 命令的详细信息，请参阅[调入 SharePoint 对象模型](/visualstudio/sharepoint/calling-into-the-sharepoint-object-models.md)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The message describing the error.
trans-unit.target: 描述错误的消息。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: 用指定的错误消息初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The SerializationInfo object that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: 保留有关引发异常的序列化对象数据的 SerializationInfo 对象。

trans-unit.source: The SerializationInfo object that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: 包含有关源或目标的上下文信息的 SerializationInfo 对象。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class with serialized data.
trans-unit.target: 用序列化数据初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: 导致当前异常的异常。

trans-unit.source: If the <c>innerException</c> parameter is not a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]), then the current exception is raised in a <see langword="catch" /> block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: 如果 innerException 参数不为空引用（在 [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)] 中为 <see langword="Nothing" />），则在处理内部异常的 <see langword="catch" /> 块中引发当前异常<c></c>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误信息和对导致此异常的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The ID of the command that threw the exception.
trans-unit.target: 引发异常的命令的 ID。

trans-unit.source: The full type name of the command class that threw the exception.
trans-unit.target: 引发异常的命令类的完整类型名称。

trans-unit.source: The original stack trace of the exception in the vssphost4.exe process.
trans-unit.target: vssphost4.exe 进程中异常的原始堆栈跟踪。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class with a specified error message, full type name, and the original stack trace.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误消息、完整类型名称和原始堆栈跟踪来初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The ID of the command that threw the exception.
trans-unit.target: 引发异常的命令的 ID。

trans-unit.source: The full type name of the command class that threw the exception.
trans-unit.target: 引发异常的命令类的完整类型名称。

trans-unit.source: The original stack trace of the exception in the vssphost4.exe process.
trans-unit.target: vssphost4.exe 进程中异常的原始堆栈跟踪。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: 导致当前异常的异常。

trans-unit.source: If the <c>innerException</c> parameter is not a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic), then the current exception is raised in a <see langword="catch" /> block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: 如果 innerException 参数不为是空引用（在 Visual Basic 中为 <see langword="Nothing" />），则在处理内部异常的 <see langword="catch" /> 块中引发当前异常<c></c>。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> class with a specified error message, full type name, the original stack trace, and a reference to the inner exception that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误消息、完整类型名称、原始堆栈跟踪和对导致该异常的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointCommandException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets the command ID that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: 获取导致异常的命令 ID。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a command ID.
trans-unit.target: 一个字符串，表示命令 id。

trans-unit.source: Gets the full type name of the command class that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: 获取导致异常的命令类的完整类型名称。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a type name.
trans-unit.target: 表示类型名称的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The SerializationInfo object to populate with data.
trans-unit.target: 要用数据填充的 SerializationInfo 对象。

trans-unit.source: The destination for this serialization.
trans-unit.target: 此序列化的目标。

trans-unit.source: See System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext for more information.
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅 System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext。

trans-unit.source: Sets <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> with information about the exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用关于异常的信息设置 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets the original exception stack trace from the vssphost4.exe process.
trans-unit.target: 获取 vssphost4.exe 进程中的原始异常堆栈跟踪。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a stack trace.
trans-unit.target: 表示堆栈跟踪的字符串。
